<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:07:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列律师协会撤销针对阿拉伯以色列律师关于加沙战争观点的听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-bar-association-drops-hearing-against-arab-israeli-lawyer-over-gaza-war-views/00000191-7f07-d06e-afdd-7f978ed80000</link><description>一名右翼活动人士因该律师在社交媒体上发帖抨击加沙战争并将极右翼部长本-格维尔称为“恐怖分子”而对他提出投诉，以色列律师协会决定取消针对他的纪律听证会</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-bar-association-drops-hearing-against-arab-israeli-lawyer-over-gaza-war-views/00000191-7f07-d06e-afdd-7f978ed80000</guid></item><item><title>人质面临死亡，以色列国防部长必须发声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/with-the-hostages-facing-death-israels-defense-chiefs-must-speak-out/00000191-7ece-dee7-a9d1-ffef9aea0000</link><description>在某些时候，军队需要打破沉默，向公众表达自己的观点：现在，人质协议是治愈和摆脱危机的唯一途径，这场危机可能会导致一场重大战争造成前所未有的伤亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 11:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/with-the-hostages-facing-death-israels-defense-chiefs-must-speak-out/00000191-7ece-dee7-a9d1-ffef9aea0000</guid></item><item><title>为了削弱内塔尼亚胡并保护其经济，伊朗正在权衡以色列袭击的时机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/in-bid-to-undermine-netanyahu-and-spare-its-economy-iran-weighs-timing-of-israel-attack/00000191-7e0f-d2f8-adf1-7e0fd0f10000</link><description>自哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚被暗杀以来已经过去了很长一段时间，加上革命卫队声明“时间站在我们一边”，这引发了西方的猜测，即伊朗不打算很快对以色列进行报复</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 08:21:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/in-bid-to-undermine-netanyahu-and-spare-its-economy-iran-weighs-timing-of-israel-attack/00000191-7e0f-d2f8-adf1-7e0fd0f10000</guid></item><item><title>“他们感到羞耻和受伤，但他们要离开”：医生正在以前所未有的规模撤离以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theyre-ashamed-but-theyre-leaving-doctors-depart-israel-on-unprecedented-scale/00000191-7b16-dfa2-a5b9-fbb799280000</link><description>以色列最大医院之一的高级管理人员警告说，这是过去几个月的新现象，我担心它只会加剧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 07:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theyre-ashamed-but-theyre-leaving-doctors-depart-israel-on-unprecedented-scale/00000191-7b16-dfa2-a5b9-fbb799280000</guid></item><item><title>在一个强大的播客中，一名记者为俄罗斯和以色列未成年性虐待案寻求正义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-powerful-podcast-journalist-seeks-justice-in-russian-israeli-underage-sex-abuse-case/00000191-7b59-daab-a3f3-fbdbac6a0000</link><description>莫斯科一所精英学校的前毕业生和暑期项目的前参与者声称，在俄罗斯和以色列，老师和辅导员对他们进行了性虐待。一名调查记者对当局不采取行动感到愤怒，正在为所谓的受害者伸张正义</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 07:25:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-powerful-podcast-journalist-seeks-justice-in-russian-israeli-underage-sex-abuse-case/00000191-7b59-daab-a3f3-fbdbac6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国导演奥弗拉·比克尔 (Ofra Bikel) 去世，享年 95 岁，他的作品释放了 13 名被错误定罪的美国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-director-whose-work-freed-13-wrongfully-convicted-americans-die-at-95/00000191-7dda-daa5-ab9f-7ffe5ed70000</link><description>七次艾美奖得主奥弗拉·比克尔 (Ofra Bikel) 的纪录片作品迫使美国司法系统宣判 13 名因未犯下的罪行而入狱的人无罪，其中包括一名被判处死刑的人。 2005 年，她告诉《国土报》：“在摄像机出现之前，没有人对这些试验感兴趣。”</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 06:54:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-director-whose-work-freed-13-wrongfully-convicted-americans-die-at-95/00000191-7dda-daa5-ab9f-7ffe5ed70000</guid></item><item><title>哈里斯告诉民主党全国委员会：我将始终确保以色列有能力保卫自己，努力结束加沙的苦难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/harris-i-will-always-ensure-israel-can-defend-itself-working-to-end-gaza-suffering/00000191-7d39-d2f8-adf1-7f3dec790000</link><description>当副总统发誓要努力让“巴勒斯坦人民实现尊严、安全、自由和自决的权利”时，全场响起最热烈的掌声。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 03:20:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/harris-i-will-always-ensure-israel-can-defend-itself-working-to-end-gaza-suffering/00000191-7d39-d2f8-adf1-7f3dec790000</guid></item><item><title>处于协议与升级的十字路口：以色列没有出口</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/at-a-crossroads-of-deal-and-escalation-israel-has-no-exit/00000191-7b93-d8d0-a7bb-fbb7d1ec0000</link><description>以色列正处于达成协议和升级之间的十字路口，而内塔尼亚胡正引领着走向深渊的边缘。在他领导下的320天战争之后，该国正处于历史上最糟糕的战略形势</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 03:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/at-a-crossroads-of-deal-and-escalation-israel-has-no-exit/00000191-7b93-d8d0-a7bb-fbb7d1ec0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔希望爆发中东战争。内塔尼亚胡将满足消耗战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-sinwar-the-war-twins-want-more-conflict-instead-of-a-cease-fire-deal/00000191-7b66-daab-a3f3-fbe617510000</link><description>本周展示了内塔尼亚胡在国内方面取得的成就：模糊了 10 月 7 日的记忆，将人质变成了一个政治问题，并让他的支持者相信，控制加沙主要路线对以色列至关重要 — — 即使付出的代价几乎是肯定的更多人质的生命</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 03:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-sinwar-the-war-twins-want-more-conflict-instead-of-a-cease-fire-deal/00000191-7b66-daab-a3f3-fbe617510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的女儿在会见内塔尼亚胡后表示，她离开时有“不好的预感”，加沙协议“不会很快达成”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-live/israel-issues-administrative-detention-orders-for-suspects-in-attacks-on-arabs-bedouin/00000191-7cda-d8bb-a1dd-7edf36a50000</link><description>黎巴嫩卫生部报告，以色列在该国南部发动的袭击造成两人死亡，其中包括儿童 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：泰尔哈法村发生的以色列袭击造成两人死亡 ■ Gallant 猛烈抨击本-格维尔呼吁解雇辛贝特酋长 ■ 以色列士兵加沙南部战斗行动中丧生 ■ 摩萨德、辛贝特酋长抵达埃及进行停火谈判 ■ 以色列军队：从加沙打捞上来的 6 名人质尸体上发现“枪声”</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 01:40:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-live/israel-issues-administrative-detention-orders-for-suspects-in-attacks-on-arabs-bedouin/00000191-7cda-d8bb-a1dd-7edf36a50000</guid></item><item><title>&amp;#39;我买了一张机票。然后我被征召去加沙执行预备役任务”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-23/ty-article/.highlight/i-bought-a-plane-ticket-then-i-got-called-up-for-reserve-duty-in-gaza/00000191-7c1d-d2f8-adf1-7e1d59cf0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名年轻的以色列人想要获得除了持有武器之外的技能，而一个家庭则陷入了假期困境</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-23/ty-article/.highlight/i-bought-a-plane-ticket-then-i-got-called-up-for-reserve-duty-in-gaza/00000191-7c1d-d2f8-adf1-7e1d59cf0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不是丘吉尔。他将被视为以色列最糟糕的总理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/netanyahu-is-no-churchill-he-will-be-remembered-as-israels-worst-prime-minister/00000191-79f6-dee7-a9d1-fdf7614c0000</link><description>历史将给比比带来使命</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 21:59:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/netanyahu-is-no-churchill-he-will-be-remembered-as-israels-worst-prime-minister/00000191-79f6-dee7-a9d1-fdf7614c0000</guid></item><item><title>道格·埃姆霍夫 (Doug Emhoff) 告诉犹太民主党人：10 月 7 日之前反犹太主义是一个大问题。现在是一场危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/doug-emhoff-antisemitism-was-a-massive-problem-before-oct-7-now-its-a-crisis/00000191-7be8-de04-af9b-7bfbbbee0001</link><description>在犹太民主委员会关于反犹太主义的活动上发表讲话时，第二位先生的出现为亲以色列民主党为期四天的活动画上句号，这些活动旨在展示哈里斯和民主党如何保持亲以色列以及最有资格打击反犹太主义</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 21:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/doug-emhoff-antisemitism-was-a-massive-problem-before-oct-7-now-its-a-crisis/00000191-7be8-de04-af9b-7bfbbbee0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯调解员希望周日举行加沙协议峰会：“取消将具有破坏性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-mediators-hoping-for-gaza-deal-summit-canceling-would-be-destructive/00000191-7bc3-de04-af9b-7bd3bc5f0000</link><description>哈马斯仍未同意参加暂定在开罗举行的会议 ■ 参与谈判的消息人士估计，内塔尼亚胡要求以色列在费城走廊存在的要求可能会破坏谈判</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 20:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-mediators-hoping-for-gaza-deal-summit-canceling-would-be-destructive/00000191-7bc3-de04-af9b-7bd3bc5f0000</guid></item><item><title>民主党全国委员会对加沙支持者关上了大门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-22/ty-article/.highlight/the-dnc-slams-the-door-on-gaza-advocates/00000191-7ac5-d15d-a3d7-7ef7c0860000</link><description>民主党全国代表大会拒绝给予一名巴勒斯坦裔美国人发言时间，这对许多亲巴勒斯坦倡导者来说是一次严峻的现实检验，因为民主党优先考虑他们的声音</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 20:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-22/ty-article/.highlight/the-dnc-slams-the-door-on-gaza-advocates/00000191-7ac5-d15d-a3d7-7ef7c0860000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特主席警告总理和部长们：犹太恐怖正在危及以色列的存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-chief-warns-pm-and-ministers-jewish-terror-is-jeopardizing-israels-existence/00000191-7b9a-de04-af9b-7b9b38070000</link><description>罗南·巴尔在一封信中警告说，“犹太恐怖分子领导人想让系统失去控制，这对以色列造成的损害是难以形容的”。他说，警察的无能和公共合法性导致了犹太恐怖主义的扩张</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 20:13:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-chief-warns-pm-and-ministers-jewish-terror-is-jeopardizing-israels-existence/00000191-7b9a-de04-af9b-7b9b38070000</guid></item><item><title>“政治性大于人道主义”：加沙援助运动使巴勒斯坦以色列人分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/more-political-than-humanitarian-aid-campaigns-for-gaza-divide-palestinian-israelis/00000191-7082-d988-a3b5-71ea1de40000</link><description>救援工作正在动员以色列各地的人们捐赠、分类和包装食品和必需品，但一些巴勒斯坦以色列人表示，他们正在考虑参与犹太-阿拉伯联合行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 19:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/more-political-than-humanitarian-aid-campaigns-for-gaza-divide-palestinian-israelis/00000191-7082-d988-a3b5-71ea1de40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医生规避法律，向父母收取巨额费用来选择婴儿的性别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bypassing-the-law-israeli-doctors-charge-parents-a-fortune-to-select-their-babys-sex/00000191-7b16-daab-a3f3-fb96bb6d0000</link><description>在以色列，性别选择是非法的。 《国土报》的一项调查显示，在国外，医生整个行业的基础就是这样做。有些家长愿意付给他们巨额费用</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 18:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bypassing-the-law-israeli-doctors-charge-parents-a-fortune-to-select-their-babys-sex/00000191-7b16-daab-a3f3-fb96bb6d0000</guid></item><item><title>“这正在杀害犹太人民，使我们分裂。内塔尼亚胡怎么会看不到这一点呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-hostage-omer-neutra-praise-biden-slam-netanyahu-at-dnc/00000191-7afe-dfa2-a5b9-fbff7a2f0000</link><description>“他完全与世隔绝”：人质奥马尔·诺伊特拉的父母赞扬拜登，猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡对释放被俘以色列人的承诺</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 18:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-hostage-omer-neutra-praise-biden-slam-netanyahu-at-dnc/00000191-7afe-dfa2-a5b9-fbff7a2f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长希望任命针对他的案件的证人担任主要职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-looking-to-appoint-witness-in-case-against-him-to-major-position/00000191-7aff-d8d0-a7bb-fbffd4150000</link><description>以色列能源部长、前外交部长伊莱·科恩因出于政治原因向不符合资格的人士发放外交护照而受到调查。他希望任命该案主要警方证人罗南·莱维（Ronen Levi）担任以色列国家能源基础设施公司的负责人</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 17:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-looking-to-appoint-witness-in-case-against-him-to-major-position/00000191-7aff-d8d0-a7bb-fbffd4150000</guid></item></channel></rss>